        <title>Driver Side Storm Glass Windows</title>
        <para>The driver side sliding window is also supplied with a sliding storm window option. The window is designed
            for use in colder climates and eliminates frost build up on the window in adverse weather. The window glass
            is a heavier and thicker design.
        </para>
